        <div1 type="summary">
            <p><add hand="#barker">Asking them to deliver two miniatures of Austin to his sister.</add></p>
        </div1>
        <div1 type="body">
            


<p>I send two likenesses of mine which I request <persName>Mr Powell</persName> to put
into the hands of my <persName>sister </persName>or <persName>Brother in law Perry</persName> Please take
care of them&#8212;they are painted on ivory in water colors and wet
will ruin them. <persName>Mr. Allsbury</persName> will put them in a box and they can
be put in your trunk edgewise so as not to crack the glass by any
weight on it.</p>

<p><persName>S. F. Austin</persName></p>

<p><persName>Mr. Peter Powell </persName>and <persName>Joseph Powel</persName></p>

<p><persName>Dn. H. Allsberry </persName>  <placeName>Pilon</placeName>.</p>


        </div1>
